code: @Override public ConfigurationProperty getConfigurationProperty(ConfigurationPropertyName name) {     boolean filtered = getFilter().test(name).     return filtered ? getSource().getConfigurationProperty(name) : null. }

@Override public ConfigurationPropertyState containsDescendantOf(ConfigurationPropertyName name) {     ConfigurationPropertyState result = this.source.containsDescendantOf(name).     if (result == ConfigurationPropertyState.PRESENT) {         // We can't be sure a contained descendant won't be filtered         return ConfigurationPropertyState.UNKNOWN.     }     return result. }
